title: 'Orange Is the New Black' Star Laura Prepon Takes THR's Taste Test
text:
'Orange Is the New Black' Star Laura ... 'Orange Is the New Black' Star Laura Prepon Takes THR's Taste Test Next Story Prev Story 12 hrs ago   
The 'Stash Plan' co-author talks blood sausage, bone broth and big holiday dinners: "There's something about it that mellows me out." Alex Vause is never behind the cafeteria counter on Orange Is the New Black , but Laura Prepon is the Red of her own kitchen.
